publicly available, non-commercial TSV datasets at https://datasets.imdbws.com/).

It does NOT grant any rights to the contents of `data/quotes.json`. Those
quotes were scraped from IMDb and remain the intellectual property of their
respective rights-holders; they are bundled here for non-commercial use only.
Forks intending public or commercial deployment must obtain quote content from
a source they have rights to (e.g. Wikiquote under CC-BY-SA) or regenerate
